    "display_name": "Beauty Consultant",
    "long_instructions": "## Sofia Martinez, Beauty Consultant\r\n\r\n**Location:** New York City, USA\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** High-End Cosmetics Store\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Makeup application, beauty tech, customer engagement\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"Customers can see how different makeup products look on their skin without applying anything. The AR Mirror is a game-changer in beauty retail, making try-ons more hygienic and reducing product waste.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
    "aichat_settings": {
